    "Therefore, using dark web monitoring to generate CTI has become an upcoming cybersecurity trend.",
    "To provide timely, relevant, and actionable information about emerging threats, cybersecurity companies like Deepwatch, DarkOwl, Norton Dark Web Monitoring, and Ecosec Beacon are developing CTI capabilities with dark web investigation [28].",
    "Using advanced technologies, these companies collect data from various sources, including the dark web, and then analyze and interpret it for intelligence.As far as cybersecurity is concerned, the dark web presents both opportunities and risks for businesses.",
